    <name>fooyin</name>
    <summary>A customisable music player</summary>
    <developer id="org.fooyin.luketaylor">
        <name>Luke Taylor</name>
    </developer>
    <description>
        <p>
            fooyin is a music player built around customisation.
            It combines flexible playback, library management, playlists, and scripting tools
            in an interface that can be rearranged from a blank canvas or adapted from preset layouts.
        </p>
        <p>
            The player is highly extensible with a plugin system and includes FooScript
            for advanced display formatting, autoplaylists, and widget behaviour.
            The playback engine also supports DSP chains, fading and crossfading.
        </p>
        <p>Key features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Fully customisable layouts and widgets, with per-widget settings and configurable shortcuts</li>
            <li>Support for major audio formats, including archives, CUE sheets, VGM, and tracker formats</li>
            <li>Internet radio discovery and remote audio stream playback</li>
            <li>Gapless playback, ReplayGain, and configurable fade and crossfade settings</li>
            <li>DSP plugin support with built-in effects such as equaliser, resampling, tempo and pitch adjustment,
                and silence skipping</li>
            <li>Audio output and device configuration</li>
            <li>Advanced library browsing with filters, tree views, and an integrated directory browser</li>
            <li>Playlist management with autoplaylists and M3U/M3U8 import and export</li>
            <li>Built-in tag editing and metadata management, including artwork embedding</li>
            <li>Artwork tools for finding, viewing, exporting, extracting, and downloading covers</li>
            <li>Visualisations including a waveform seekbar, spectrum, and VU meter</li>
            <li>Lyrics search, editing, syncing, and display, with configurable presentation for synced lyrics panels</li>
            <li>FooScript-powered scripting and display tools for rich formatting throughout the interface</li>
            <li>Plugin-based extensibility for widgets, decoders, tag readers, DSPs, and others</li>
            <li>Desktop integration with MPRIS, scrobbling services, and Discord Rich Presence</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
